    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1930-04-08T16:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1930-04-08T16:00:00-05:00" n="658"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d658">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.51/5241: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Minister in China</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Johnson</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1930-04-08T16:00:00-05:00"
                            >April 8, 1930—4 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>124. Your 247, April 3, 9 p.m., last paragraph. As you are aware, the Department
                    is desirous that definite steps be taken as soon as practicable toward
                    settlement of outstanding obligations of the Chinese Government to American
                    citizens. Department therefore authorizes you to urge the National Government to
                    take, without further delay, some practical measure for the relief of American
                    creditors. While authorizing you to make such changes as you may desire, the
                    Department suggests a note in substance as follows:</p>
                <p>[Here follows text used as basis for note to the Chinese Minister for Foreign
                    Affairs, dated April 12, 1930, printed as enclosure to despatch No. 147, <hi
                        rend="italic">infra.</hi>]</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Cotton</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
